title: Griffith University team all welcome
body:
Hi i am currently studying at Griffith University and was looking to start a number of teams to enter into the championships 
Let me know if interested and we can go from there
There is also a facebook page called "Griffith LoL Community" which you can join
Join the LoL chat "Griffith"
Alternatively add me "RustyJesus"

replies.body: Hey, i'm studying in QIBT, a part of griffith university. I tried joining the facebook page but it says invalid email address. Help me join the community!

Hey, I'm actually hoping to come to Griffith next year for that crash hot new computer science degree ;) 
I'm a lowly gold player but it would be great to get to start knowing people down on brisvegas.
I am also at grifftafe and am keen to join a griff team add me in game
